{"data":[{"date":"15:42 15/08","title":"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sterling gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch h\u00ecnh x\u0103m m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7y \u00fd ngh\u0129a","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/tien-dao-sterling-giai-thich-hinh-xam-moi-day-y-nghia.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"5525","checkdouble":"194543"},{"date":"15:48 15/08","title":"C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italia su\u00fdt b\u1ecf m\u1ea1ng v\u00ec tai n\u1ea1n s\u1eadp c\u1ea7u","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/15/cuu-tuyen-thu-italia-suyt-bo-mang-vi-tai-nan-sap-cau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Domenico Criscito cho bi\u1ebft, anh \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \"\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ch\u00faa\" trong v\u1ee5 s\u1eadp c\u1ea7u Morandi \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Genoa khi\u1ebfn \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 35 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi\u1ec7t m\u1ea1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Domenico Criscito l\u00e1i xe b\u0103ng qua c\u1ea7u Morandi tr\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cao t\u1ed1c A10 t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Genoa. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u00f2n \u0111\u0103ng l\u00ean trang Instagram c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi \u0111ang m\u01b0a r\u1ea5t to. 10 ph\u00fat sau, kho\u1ea3ng 200m c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfc c\u1ea7u Morandi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ed5 s\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fac 11h30 gi\u1edd \u0111ia ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u00eda ch\u00ednh quy\u1ec1n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Genoa x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bi k\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Genoa. Trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n k\u00e9m may m\u1eafn c\u00f3 1 em b\u00e9, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ebft ngay trong nh\u00e0 \u1edf ph\u00eda d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/criscito1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng 24 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Italia \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea5n an ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Instagram: \"Khi t\u00f4i \u0111i qua c\u1ea7u Morandi ch\u1eebng 10 ph\u00fat th\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed5 s\u1eadp. May m\u1eafn l\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng sao. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00e1c n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n thi\u1ec7t m\u1ea1ng trong tai n\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc n\u00e0y\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ec1u c\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y, Genoa theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi AC Milan \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Serie A 2018/19 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 Hai, 20/8. Tuy nhi\u00ean, CLB Genoa \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ho\u00e3n bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp sau s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f4ng t\u00e1c c\u1ee9u h\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tri\u1ec3n khai nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t trong c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed5 n\u00e1t.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5524","checkdouble":"194544"},{"date":"14:05 15/08","title":"HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Nepal.</h2><h2>HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/1080327.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u00f4ng&nbsp;Hajime Moriyasu</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Nepal. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi x\u00e9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: &ldquo;\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u00f9y th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00fac 3 ho\u1eb7c 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt kh\u00e1c \u0111i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo \u00f4ng Moriyasu, n\u1ebfu Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai th\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Nepal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u00ecm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 v\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u, bao g\u1ed3m Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai 16/8, Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Olympic Paksitan l\u00fac 16h00 v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nepal di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 19h00.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam-472-194532.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam-472-194532.html\">Olympic Nepal \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng thua Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Pakistan.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5523","checkdouble":"194534"},{"date":"14:21 15/08","title":"Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/chan-sut-son-heungmin-canh-bao-dong-doi-truoc-them-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 quan t\u1ea1i ASIAD&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean mu\u1ed9n nh\u1ea5t l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sau khi anh v\u1eeba c\u00f9ng Tottenham gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 b\u1ea3y v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ban \u0111\u1ea7u, Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 sau khi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Tuy v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 xin ph\u00e9p ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Tottenham bay th\u1eb3ng sang T\u00e2y Java t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ngay sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Newcastle.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Chan-sut-Son-Heung-min-nhac-nho-dong-doi-truoc-them-ASIAD-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Son Heung-Min mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xem m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea5m HCV 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Son Heung-min c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 1 trong 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hwang Ui-Jo c\u1ee7a Gamba Osaka v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Jo Hyeon-Woo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y song ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Anh v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111i m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i xem m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eebng b\u1ecb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u1ea1 \u1edf World Cup, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y&rdquo;. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do s\u1edbm c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Indonesia, Son Heung-min cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 ASIAD tr\u00ean chuy\u1ebfn bay \u0111\u1ebfn Indonesia v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n khi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cho h\u1ecd l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn h\u1ecd c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min t\u1edbi v\u1edbi ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Theo lu\u1eadt H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, m\u1ecdi nam c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tu\u1ed5i 27 song v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh HCV ch\u00e2u \u00c1 hay Olympic.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 xem th\u00eam k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5522","checkdouble":"194535"},{"date":"15:00 15/08","title":"Th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/thong-tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-xuan-truong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m th\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xuan Truong\" title=\"Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/thong-tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-xuan-truong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 lo ng\u1ea1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra trong hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL b\u1ecb \u0111au \u1edf ch\u00e2n l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean lo ng\u1ea1i anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m - Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo thay Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb l\u00fd do chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch th\u00eam v\u00ec l\u00fd do thay Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edfi&nbsp;HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0 nh\u1eadp h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, so v\u1edbi Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00ec H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park tung H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t &quot;s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda&quot; gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng&nbsp;ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Tuy\u00ean Quang v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D ASIAD.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d-168-194534.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d-168-194534.html\">HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Nepal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n s\u00fat 11m cho &lsquo;\u0111\u00e0n em&rsquo; C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m, c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf l\u1eabn BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:&#10;16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5521","checkdouble":"194537"},{"date":"15:33 15/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan.</h2><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 14/8 v\u1eeba qua, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan. N\u1ebfu C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f2n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo, b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/olympic-viet-nam-vs-pakistan-8-153424042905491724090.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho \u0110T\u00a0Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Sportalkorea\u00a0\u0111\u01b0a tin: Tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu 2 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edd Chosun l\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8: \"Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, so v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 cho k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi sang ghi h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u1eeba qua. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam-472-194532.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam-472-194532.html\">Olympic Nepal \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng thua Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Pakistan.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-292-194503.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-292-194503.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan: Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn khi c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5520","checkdouble":"194540"},{"date":"16:21 15/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ec1u 15/8, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u0110T Olympic Nepal.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Nepal \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eed th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 khi\u1ebfn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh Nepal. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo hy v\u1ecdng Nepal s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 tho\u00e1ng h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/binhluan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo mong ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Olympic Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc chi\u1ec1u 15/8, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i: \u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, n\u1ebfu th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, n\u1ebfu th\u1ebf th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Park c\u0169ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y: \u201cD\u00f9 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nepal kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c b\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Nepal.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">rong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Indonesia th\u00ec Nepal ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t \u00edt. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng? Hay ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c? Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e0i s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi U23 Pakistan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn\u00a0U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e0i s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Pakistan.\u00a0T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111a s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nhau t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng hay V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m n\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Nepal l\u00fac 19h00, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Pakistan l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u 16/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung-472-194545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung-472-194545.html\">U23 Nepal c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n nh\u01b0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng</span><br>\r\nU23 Nepal, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng: Kiran Chemjong Limbu.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo?</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d-168-194534.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d-168-194534.html\">HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Nepal.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5519","checkdouble":"194546"},{"date":"14:49 15/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Barcelona vs Boca Juniors 23h15 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-barcelona-vs-boca-juniors-23h15-ngay-158-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barcelona vs Boca Juniors l\u00fac 23h15 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 Joan Gamper 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Barcelona vs Boca Juniors 23h15 ng\u00e0y 158 Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Barcelona vs Boca Juniors 23h15 ng\u00e0y 158 Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/bar-boca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barcelona vs Boca Juniors</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>Barcelona vs Boca Juniors: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\u1ede 5 tr\u1eadn tranh Joan Gamper Trophy g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Barca \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, h\u1ecd v\u00f9i d\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Chapecoense c\u1ee7a Brazil 5 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, trong 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00f3i tr\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalunya ghi t\u1edbi 25 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, trong khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Sampdoria 3-2 n\u0103m 2016.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 ch\u1ec7ch cho\u1ea1c trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, nh\u01b0ng khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, Barca \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla 2-1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u1edf Morocco \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2018 nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a HLV Valverde, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng xem tr\u1eadn tranh Joan Gamper Trophy \u0111\u00eam nay l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu. Barca s\u1ebd tung ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 Lionel Messi, Luis Suarez hay Ivan Rakitic\u2026 C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Boca Juniors \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef c\u00fap l\u1ea1i Nou Camp, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Argentina \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 10 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i (th\u1eafng 6, h\u00f2a 4) v\u00e0 \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Carlos Tevez hay Cristian Pavon.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 b\u00e0n hi\u1ec7p 1<br>\r\n18/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Barca c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean trong hi\u1ec7p 1. C\u1ea3 8 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Boca Juniors \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng hi\u1ec7p 1. Do v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00eam nay c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5518","checkdouble":"194538"},{"date":"15:07 15/08","title":"Zizou \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay Jose Mourinho \u1edf M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd b\u00e1o danh ti\u1ebfng L'Equipe (Ph\u00e1p) v\u1eeba loan tin r\u1eb1ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Zinedine Zidane mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \"gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng\" m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u1edf Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chia tay Real Madrid, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn Man Utd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t thay t\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u1eefa d\u00f2ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u lung lay do th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p\u00a0BL\u0110\u00a0Man Utd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3, th\u00ec Zidane s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 Zidane s\u1ebd thay Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 Zidane s\u1ebd thay Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/zidane-den-mu-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn \"gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng\" \u1edf MU m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111ang ng\u1ed3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p HLV th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 tin t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 \"\u0111\u00f3ng th\u1ebf\" Benitez v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ban \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi Real trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00ecm HLV\u00a0m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng Zizou \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd r\u1eb1ng Real Madrid l\u00e0 CLB \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0m HLV\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Zidane (tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1eafm vai tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd cho HLV Ancelotti \u1edf Bernabeu). K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, \"Zizou \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebf\" \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u00e0nh 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c Zidane b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Real ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y sau khi c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa hattrick th\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh h\u1ed3i g\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCLB m\u00e0 Zidane t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Zidane, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau khi L\u00e3o b\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 L\u0110B\u0110 Qatar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng m\u1eddi HLV 46 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng theo tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb t\u1edd L'Equire, Zidane l\u1ea1i h\u1ee9ng th\u1ee7 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League, m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Man Utd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o n\u0103m th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Old Trafford trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1 h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n. C\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd do thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. Ph\u00eda ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n, Mourinho th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 gi\u00f4ng b\u00e3o \u1edf c\u00e1c CLB \u00f4ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, MU g\u1eb7p may khi th\u1eafng Leicester 2-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai kh\u00e1c, Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League 2018/19. V\u00e0 Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft, \u0111\u01b0a vinh quang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho, MU ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 cho HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-lai-khien-mu-dung-ngoi-khong-yen-voi-phat-bieu-ve-pogba-172-194533.html\">Barca l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn MU \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-thua-xa-man-city-va-liverpool-172-194512.html\">M.U thua xa Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-se-khong-ban-pogba-cho-barca-172-194472.html\">MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ander-herrera-goi-y-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-mu-172-194468.html\">Ander Herrera mang tin vui \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/darmian-nang-nac-doi-roi-mu-172-194460.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>T\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)</p>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5517","checkdouble":"194539"},{"date":"17:44 15/08","title":"\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" MU b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/5/zaha-bao-tin-buon-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Wilfried Zaha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Crystal Palace.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park trong 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Zaha m\u1edbi k\u00fd k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Crystal Palace s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2022/23.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nZaha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Tottenham ho\u1eb7c Chelsea m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, anh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Palace trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Zaha b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Zaha b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Tien-ve-Zaha-bao-tin-buon-cho-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Zaha gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Palace</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nZaha \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 44 b\u00e0n trong 288 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Palace k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u0103m 2010. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1edf Premier League r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Fulham cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Steve Parrish c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace cho bi\u1ebft: <em>\u201cZaha \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn l\u00ean \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ebfn Selhurst Park t\u1eeb khi m\u1edbi 4 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 12. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1eeba k\u00fd k\u1ebft cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai ph\u00eda. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf Palace, c\u00e1c C\u0110V v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Zaha. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nZaha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd chia tay \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Roy Hodgson sau khi \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao trong 12 th\u00e1ng qua. Anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 b\u00e0n \u1edf Premier League, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Zaha nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3 v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Christian Benteke.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/bakayoko-tri-an-chelsea-sau-khi-gia-nhap-ac-milan-184-194523.html\">Bakayoko tri \u00e2n Chelsea sau khi gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/than-dong-chelsea-co-the-tro-thanh-mbappe-thu-hai-172-194521.html\">Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Mbappe th\u1ee9 hai</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5516","checkdouble":"194549"},{"date":"09:17 15/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khen ng\u1ee3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-chau-a-khen-ngoi-chien-thang-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u \u00c1 theo d\u00f5i s\u00e1t sao c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Pakistan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, trang FOX Sports phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eb7ng cho V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e2y b\u00fat Gabriel Tan cho r\u1eb1ng, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang d\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i tri\u1ebft l\u00fd ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/vn-15342604637281618228882.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, t\u1ea1o th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o so v\u1edbi Pakistan v\u00e0 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 3-0. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng, nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng. N\u1ebfu gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho Nepal l\u1eabn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Gabriel Tan, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1ecf con Quang H\u1ea3i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi ch\u01a1i b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9, s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o d\u00f9 b\u1ecb k\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Sohu c\u1ee7a Trung Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD. \"Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m. M\u1ecdi con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd so v\u1edbi Pakistan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 Messi c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 ASIAD. Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSiamSport c\u0169ng so s\u00e1nh gi\u1eefa U23 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Asiad: \"U23 Th\u00e1i Lan ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb Qatar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 l\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. H\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 nghi\u1ec1n n\u00e1t U23 Pakistan 3-0.\"<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u1edd b\u00e1o nh\u01b0 Goal phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Th\u00e1i Lan, STN Sports c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, \u0111\u01b0a tin v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng, s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfn xa.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 d\u01b0 \u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-thay-doi-ke-hoach-tap-luyen-sau-tran-thang-pakistan-168-194505.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Pakistan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-khong-con-co-hoi-da-11m-duoi-thoi-hlv-park-hang-seo-168-194504.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-292-194503.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan: Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong-168-194500.html\">Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5515","checkdouble":"194524"},{"date":"09:40 15/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 15/8: Paul Scholes nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/diem-tin-sang-158-paul-scholes-nhan-xet-buon-ve-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Scholes nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 MU, Tottenham d\u1eddi ng\u00e0y m\u1edf c\u1eeda SV\u0110,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 15/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi sang Juventus c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n Cristiano Ronaldo, Marcelo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \"gi\u1edd ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y\" khi \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Real Madrid chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Atletico t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 158 Paul Scholes nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 158 Paul Scholes nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/scholes.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Paul Scholes \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League c\u1ee7a Man Utd.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng Paul Scholes nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Man Utd v\u1eabn \"r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf b\u00e9\", b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1eabn k\u00e9m so v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 37 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng Samuel Eto'o ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. \"B\u00e1o \u0111en\" m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Qatar SC, m\u1ed9t CLB t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Qatar. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 CLB th\u1ee9 13 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Eto'o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eb3ng ai \u1edf Liverpool ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Naby Keita trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi West Ham, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Guinea t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Premier League c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0a th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1c 31/8, khi c\u00e1c CLB s\u1ebd b\u1ecf phi\u1ebfu trong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. \u1ede m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018, k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Premier League k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 9/8, tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Koke cho r\u1eb1ng ngay c\u1ea3 khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Real Madrid v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Atletico ph\u1ea3i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ghi b\u00e0n g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, N'Golo Kante kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u01b0 v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 \u1edf ph\u00eda sau \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"San moi cua Tottenham dang trong qua trinh hoan thien va du kien mo cua vao ngay 15/9.\" title=\"S\u00e2n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn m\u1edf c\u1eeda v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15/9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-he-2018-Mua-khong-noi,-ban-chang-xong!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>S\u00e2n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1ebd m\u1edf c\u1eeda mu\u1ed9n h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ban \u0111\u1ea7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3i d\u1eddi th\u1eddi gian m\u1edf c\u1eeda s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1edbi do v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 an to\u00e0n, thay v\u00ec l\u1ecbch d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15/9. Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1n kho\u1ea3ng 800 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y SV\u0110 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \"hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018-19, Luke Shaw g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap Man Utd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1. Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft ch\u01a1i hay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, Luke Shaw cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi\u00a0Jonny Marsh, chuy\u00ean gia dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi De Bruyne, Kyle Walker v\u00e0 John Terry \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Gabi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \"c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn\" khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Thibaut Courtois kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn trong bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 15/8:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-chau-a-khen-ngoi-chien-thang-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-2018-168-194524.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khen ng\u1ee3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-liverpool-khong-phai-so-mot-nhung-se-danh-bai-so-mot-172-194517.html\">Klopp: Liverpool kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-atletico-madrid-tiet-lo-ly-do-tu-choi-gia-nhap-man-utd-172-194516.html\">Sao Atletico Madrid ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/lionel-messi-khong-len-tuyen-argentina-da-giao-huu-184-194514.html\">Lionel Messi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jurgen-klopp-canh-bao-liverpool-172-194513.html\">Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool:West Ham \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i M.U hay Man City</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5514","checkdouble":"194526"},{"date":"10:29 15/08","title":"Diego Simeone ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/diego-simeone-truoc-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mang t\u00ednh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><h2>Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eb1ng x\u00fac c\u1ea3m<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2 2018 gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Atletico Madri mang r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Julen Lopetegui, sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Zinedine Zidane v\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/diego-simeone-truoc-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Atletico trong th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Gabi c\u1ee7a Atletico th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Courtois tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 mang \u0111\u1ebfn \"n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \"\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Atletico Madrid gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Antoine Griezmann, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Gelson Martins, Thomas Lemar hay Santiago Arias. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Diego Simeone cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi si\u00eau sao s\u1ed1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t l\u00ean ngay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp\" - HLV Simeone \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: \"R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng h\u1ecd\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m ai h\u1ebft. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn theo nh\u01b0 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Diego Simeone s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y khi v\u1eabn v\u01b0\u1edbng \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft t\u1ea1i Europa League g\u1eb7p Arsenal. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Atletico s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Atletico Madrid m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-atletico-madrid-tiet-lo-ly-do-tu-choi-gia-nhap-man-utd-172-194516.html\">Sao Atletico Madrid ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-valencia-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-atletico-madrid-180-194372.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Valencia chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao Atletico Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-madrid-chinh-thuc-co-tien-dao-moi-180-194137.html\">Atletico Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-bat-ngo-chuyen-huong-sang-godin-172-194125.html\">MU t\u00ednh g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Atletico</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-tien-dao-moi-180-193893.html\">Atletico \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5513","checkdouble":"194528"}]}